cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization of radiology findings. The use of neural sequence-to-sequence learning also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of image analysis in radiology reports could also place it in the sub-categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
